Title: Attack At The Temple of the Jade Serpent
Description:
Darkness enshrouds the Temple of the Jade Serpent, and Yu'Lon's priests beseech us for aid.

They hold the sha in check, but just barely.

You may be able to turn the tide, $c.
ObjectivesText: Speak to Elder Sage Tai-Feng at the Jade Temple Grounds in The Jade Forest.
